Server creation -Node and Express

BASIC COMMANDS

1.CREATING package.json-npm init
2.INSTALL Express - npm i Express
3.Instal JWT-npm i jsonewebtoken

BASIC STEPS
-----------------------

1 creating a folder
2 creating package.json file
3 install Express
4 creating index.js file
5  import express inside index file
6 create app using express
7 setup port number
8 Resolving http request

9 HTTP Response code 
--------------------------
1xx-Information
2xx-success
3xx-Redirection
4xx-cilent error
5xx-server error

